</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">慢慢喝，大声说</span></p><p begin="1:33.367" end="1:35.346" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.367" end="1:33.794">Enough</span> <span begin="1:33.794" end="1:34.363">soul,</span> <span begin="1:34.363" end="1:34.548">we</span> <span begin="1:34.548" end="1:34.669">could</span> <span begin="1:34.669" end="1:35.074">sell</span> <span begin="1:35.074" end="1:35.346">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">灵魂管够，我们能让全场售空</span></p><p begin="1:36.155" end="1:41.356" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.155" end="1:36.457">Can</span> <span begin="1:36.457" end="1:36.965">you</span> <span begin="1:37.736" end="1:38.018">hold</span> <span begin="1:38.018" end="1:38.323">me</span> <span begin="1:38.689" end="1:38.971">down</span> <span begin="1:38.971" end="1:39.168">for</span> <span begin="1:39.168" end="1:39.469">one</span> <span begin="1:39.469" end="1:39.765">night,</span> <span begin="1:39.892" end="1:40.148">like</span> <span begin="1:40.148" end="1:40.342">I</span> <span begin="1:40.342" end="1:40.609">got</span> <span begin="1:40.609" end="1:40.874">three</span> <span begin="1:40.874" end="1:41.356">strikes?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能不能陪我一整晚，就当我已经没有退路？</span></p><p begin="1:41.917" end="1:47.678" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.917" end="1:42.109">I</span> <span begin="1:42.109" end="1:42.492">need</span> <span begin="1:42.492" end="1:42.837">you</span> <span begin="1:43.396" end="1:43.497">to</span> <span begin="1:43.497" end="1:43.981">free</span> <span begin="1:43.981" end="1:44.330">me,</span> <span begin="1:45.457" end="1:45.653">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:45.653" end="1:45.889">a</span> <span begin="1:45.889" end="1:46.274">prison</span> <span begin="1:46.274" end="1:46.741">inside</span> <span begin="1:46.741" end="1:47.098">my</span> <span begin="1:47.098" end="1:47.678">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml